text: Suqualena Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. Suqualena is a name derived from the Choctaw language purported to mean (sources vary) "creek on whose banks are camps" or "poor hog". A variant name is "Sookalena Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Lauderdale County, Mississippi
title: Suqualena Creek
